Emails and attachments are for informational purposes only and should not be construed as a solicitation or offer to buy or sell any securities or financial instruments. No liability is accepted for any loss arising from viruses, corruption or interception to emails, nor for errors or omissions in their contents, nor for any personal or private messages sent by employees or partners.  Emails should not be relied upon as giving any legal or tax advice; you should seek your own professional advice on these matters. Past performance is not necessarily indicative of future performance. No liability whatsoever is accepted for any loss arising from the use of emails or attachments, or otherwise arising in connection with them.

